          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "By default, MapKit JS places the callout bubble slightly (1 pixel) above the top-center point of the annotation element.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To choose a different placement, provide an offset point where positive x-values move the callout bubble to the left, and positive y-values move the callout bubble up. For example, to leave a 5-pixel margin between the top of the annotation and the bottom of the callout, use a callout offset of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "DOMPoint(0, 5)",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
